Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.84,0:24:11.63,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\pos(148,88)}火憐DaZe！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.53,0:24:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,月火Da☆Yo！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,兩個人合在一起就是Fire Sisters！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:12.47,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\pos(504,88)}月火DaYo！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:14.76,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,117.333)}我們是Fire Sisters！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.70,0:24:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,偽物語和貓物語（黑）和大家分別了一段時間之後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.83,0:24:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我們終於又從本篇回到了預告這個舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:20.73,Note,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,165.333)}物語系列終於開幕！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:20.73,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\pos(537,326.667)}兩季長篇
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:20.73,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,298.667)}期待&Fresher
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:20.73,NoteVertical,,0,0,0,,{\pos(127,286.667)}稍稍有些不安
